continuing a family tradition of serving authentic italian food to the fellsmere community.
Dear Valued Customers and Community,
​
We are thrilled to share some great news with you about our family business. My husband (Brett) and I (Raffaella) are now the proud owners of Giuseppe's Italian Restaurant in Fellsmere! I am a third-generation Giambanco, continuing the Giuseppe's legacy my father, Robert, and Nonno/Grandfather, Giuseppe, originally founded in the Roseland Plaza back in 1983! We will continue to serve the same delicious recipes my Nonno Giuseppe and Uncle Eddie have served the last 30 years here in Fellsmere! We welcome you to visit, and if the timing is right, you may get to meet our two beautiful daughters, Aurelia and Alessia, hanging out at the pizza shop with us.
​
Thank you for your continued patronage, and we look forward to meeting and getting to know you all!
​
All our best,
Raffaella & Brett
